Not a particularly compelling reason to get an Xbox. 9 of those games will be available on PC. 6 of them are FPS games, which are always better on PC due to easy modification and keyboard &amp; mouse controls. SWG will be exactly like it is on PC, and PSO is identical on GC, PS2, PC and Xbox. I don't know what basis you have for saying EtM will be best on the Xbox. So out of all that, you've got Ninja Gaiden and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>maybe</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Enter the Matrix.<br>
